            {
              "name": "dialogues",
              "type": "string",
              "value": "[\"You've walked through the darkness. Through the fragments of a world that forgot itself.\",\"She's waiting. But before you go to her... I need to know.\",{\"type\":\"choice\",\"question\":\"Do you still remember who you are?\",\"options\":[{\"text\":\"Asahina Mafuyu\",\"reward\":{\"type\":\"hp_up\",\"value\":10},\"nextDialogue\":[\"I see... That name still holds meaning for you.\",\"Then take this. You'll need it for what lies ahead.\",\"Go. End this.\"]},{\"text\":\"I... don't know\",\"nextDialogue\":[\"...I see.\",\"Perhaps that's more honest than clinging to a name.\",\"Go anyway. Maybe you will remember at the end.\"]}]}]"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
